apt-get install build-essential cmake htop libbsd-dev
apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-gfx1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev
apt-get install libopencv-dev libopencv-core-dev libopencv-imgproc-dev libopencv-objdetect-dev
apt-get install libsqlite3-dev libgnutls28-dev libcurl4-gnutls-dev libgcrypt20-dev libxml2-dev libpam0g-dev

* gnutls and gcrypt (SSL support)
* pthreads (threading support)


* libxml2 (WebDAV support)
* libpam (HTTP Basic Auth support using PAM)
* C++ compiler
* Systemd (support for listening on systemd sockets)
* sqlite3 (sqlite3 session backend)
* hiredis (Redis session backend)



Build libonion:

cd ..
git clone https://github.com/davidmoreno/onion.git 
mkdir onion/build
cd onion/build
cmake ..
make
sudo make install



Build WiringPi:

cd ..
git clone git://git.drogon.net/wiringPi
cd wiringPi
./build
make status


